  <summary date="2021-10-22T15:11:01Z" status="Introduced in House">Pipeline and LNG Facility Cybersecurity Preparedness Act

This bill requires the Department of Energy to implement a program to ensure the security, resiliency, and survivability of natural gas pipelines, hazardous liquid pipelines, and liquefied natural gas facilities.</summary>
